<db:abstract>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qwaylandquickshellsurfaceitem.xml">QWaylandQuickShellSurfaceItem</db:link> class provides a Qt Quick item that represents a <db:link xlink:href="qwaylandshellsurface.xml">QWaylandShellSurface</db:link>.</db:para>
